      "Keep the preview logic local to the ownership classifier and its tests.",
      "Preserve the current approval_required handling for restricted writes.",
      "Do not change the file ownership policy format."
    ],
    "rationale": "Forbidden paths should be visible as blocked or unowned in the preview so the workflow does not overstate local ownership."
  },
